OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FA victim of sexual abuse at the
OL,8,Fnotorious Kincora Boys Home is to
OL,9,Freceive a #100,000 payout.
OL,11,FThe settlement reached in Richard
OL,12,FKerr's civil action also involved
OL,13,Fpolice and two Stormont departments
OL,14,Fexpressing "deep regret" about his
OL,15,Fchildhood exploitation.
OL,17,FMr Kerr, 64, sued over claims he was
OL,18,Ftrafficked and abused while a resident
OL,19,Fat the home in east Belfast and other
OL,20,Finstitutions during the 1960s and
OL,21,F1970s.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
