FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FA paedophile ring subjected him to
OL,8,Fyears of rape and molestation in a
OL,9,Fcampaign covered up by the British
OL,10,Fstate, it was alleged.
OL,12,FDamages were sought against the
OL,13,FDepartment of Health, the Department
OL,14,Fof Justice, the Police Service of
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland and the Secretary of
OL,16,FState for the Home Department.
OL,18,FThe lawsuit involved claims for
OL,19,Fassault and battery, misfeasance in
OL,20,Fpublic office, breach of statutory
OL,21,Fduty and negligence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
