OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FAn agreed statement read out on behalf
OL,8,Fof the PSNI, Department of Health and
OL,9,FDepartment of Justice acknowledged the
OL,10,FHistorical Institutional Abuse (HIA)
OL,11,FInquiry previously found Mr Kerr was
OL,12,Fsexually exploited and abused as a boy
OL,13,Fand young man, with no doubt about the
OL,14,Fserious adverse impact on his life.
OL,16,F"While these defendants do not accept
OL,17,Fliability, the plaintiff should not
OL,18,Fhave been subjected to any abuse
OL,19,Fwhatsoever, and it is a matter of deep
OL,20,Fregret to these defendants that he
OL,21,Fwas," the statement added.
OL,26,@xD@AOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FMr Kerr, who now lives in Dallas,
OL,8,FTexas, spent more than two years at
OL,9,Fthe now demolished Kincora home.
OL,11,FHe also sued over his earlier
OL,12,Ftreatment in care at Williamson House
OL,13,Fin north Belfast, and a later period
OL,14,Fat a borstal in County Down.
OL,16,FDuring his childhood he was allegedly
OL,17,Fplied with alcohol and sexually
OL,18,Fassaulted by a number of men on a
OL,19,Fnumber of occasions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
