FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FCourt papers set out claims of being
OL,8,Ftaken to hotels in Belfast, Portrush
OL,9,Fand Bangor to be abused.
OL,11,FAccording to his case he was also
OL,12,Fattacked while working at horse
OL,13,Fstables near Larne.
OL,15,FAnother alleged incident involved
OL,16,Fbeing molested by a former soldier
OL,17,Fafter being sent to his home in west
OL,18,FBelfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FMr Kerr further claimed he had been
OL,8,Fput on ferries to England, where he
OL,9,Fwas picked up by men and taken to
OL,10,Flocations in Manchester and London.
OL,12,FAs part of the action it was alleged
OL,13,Fthat previous investigations failed to
OL,14,Fexpose the full abuse at Kincora,
OL,15,Falong with the suspected knowledge and
OL,16,Frole of British state agents.
OL,18,FHis lawyers also claimed failures by
OL,19,Fthe Royal Ulster Constabulary to
OL,20,Fproperly probe events at the home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
