FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FMr Kerr's solicitor, Kevin Winters,
OL,8,Fpraised his courage in taking the case
OL,9,Fover "profound and lasting harm"
OL,10,Fsuffered during childhood.
OL,12,FSince then he has lived with the
OL,13,Fconsequences of serious oversight,
OL,14,Fsafeguarding and investigative
OL,15,Fshortcomings identified by the HIA
OL,16,FInquiry, the solicitor said.
OL,26,@qD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
