OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1782850701
OL,3,CKincora sex abuse victim receives
OL,4,C#100k as authorities express 'deep
OL,5,Cregret'
OL,7,FMr Winters added: "Despite decades of
OL,8,Fpublic discussion concerning Kincora
OL,9,Fand related institutions, Richard has
OL,10,Fnever before received a personal
OL,11,Fapology acknowledging the abuse he
OL,12,Fsuffered and its devastating impact
OL,13,Fupon him.
OL,15,F"Today's settlement cannot undo the
OL,16,Fpast, but it brings a measure of
OL,17,Fclosure and recognition that has been
OL,18,Flong overdue."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
